<para>This function performs platform initialization including enabling caches and initializing UART. If running outside of SDK, it can also call ps7_init() or psu_init() for Zynq-7000 or Zynq UltraScale+ respectively (requires uncommenting and including appropriate header files).</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para>None</para></simplesect>
